description: Step into a stunning South Boston penthouse where sophistication meets convenience. This 1,467 sq. ft. floor-through unit offers breathtaking skyline views and abundant natural light. Designed for entertaining, the sleek open-concept living, dining, and kitchen area features floor-to-ceiling windows. The modern kitchen boasts custom cabinetry, high-end stainless steel appliances, and a waterfall quartz island. The primary suite is a private retreat with a custom closet and spa-like en-suite bath. A spacious second bedroom with built-ins and a rare bonus office/flex room with a window and closet adds versatility. Gleaming hardwood floors enhance the warm, modern aesthetic. A private rear deck offers a perfect city view, while a deeded garage space ensures convenience. Experience the best of South Boston, steps from top dining, shops, and more!
